description:
A model of Asahina Aoi from Danganronpa 1. Trained on NAI.

See samples for good prompts. Clothes are very customizable. Also, this model doesn't requires a trigger word.

I'm planning to do every Danganronpa characters, tell me who you wants first! Check my other Danganronpa LoRAs and review them if you like them.
